Class RowModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
      • com.theforce.programutviklingsepisodeIV.RowModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.table.TableModel

    public class RowModel
extends javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
    Container class that keeps track of all rows

    Keeps track of rows position, if they get deleted, created etc... It also keeps track of the amouth of rows

    Author:
    Hans Martin Bragen, John Hoegh-Omdal, Jehans Storvik
